### Админ-панель (ROLE_ADMIN)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/admin/dashboard
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Статистика системы (ROLE_ADMIN)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/admin/stats
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Моя команда (ROLE_COACH, ROLE_MAIN_COACH)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/coach/my-team
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Расписание (ROLE_COACH, ROLE_MAIN_COACH)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/coach/schedule
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}